title: Seattle Seahawks vs. Cincinnati Bengals: Live updates, score, game chat
text:
The Seattle Seahawks kick off Week 5 of the 2015 NFL season with a trip to the Cincinnati to face the Cincinnati Bengals on Sunday.
More : TV channel and how to watch this game online
Follow along as we bring you live updates and analysis from the game from kickoff through the final whistle in the comments section below. Have thoughts on how Pete Carroll and the Seahawks are performing? Don't hesitate to jump in on the live updates and chat with us as the game rolls along.
